<view class="login-page">
  <view class="login-hero">
    <view class="brand-row">
      <view class="brand-mark"></view>
      <view>
        <view class="brand-name">儿童成长小助手</view>
        <view class="brand-tag caption">让每一次陪伴都被看见</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="slogan h1">记录成长，让陪伴更轻松</view>
    <view class="caption muted">支持多场景家庭，自动整理老师与家长的碎片记录。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="form-wrapper">
    <view class="form-card">
      <view class="h3">微信一键体验</view>
      <view class="caption muted">临时测试入口，将为你创建体验账号“安安爸爸”。</view>

      <view class="gap16"></view>

      <button class="primary-btn main-btn" bindtap="onQuickLogin" loading="{{loading}}">
        一键体验登录（安安爸爸）
      </button>

      <view class="divider-text">
        <view class="line"></view>
        <view class="caption muted">或使用账号密码登录</view>
        <view class="line"></view>
      </view>

      <view class="h3">家长账号登录</view>
      <view class="caption muted">第一次使用？直接设置一个昵称和密码即可。</view>

      <view class="gap16"></view>

      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">用户名</view>
        <input class="input" placeholder="例如：xinkai / 妈妈 / 爸爸" bindinput="onUsernameInput" value="{{username}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <view class="field-label">密码</view>
        <input class="input" placeholder="请输入密码" password="true" bindinput="onPasswordInput" value="{{password}}" />
      </view>

      <view class="gap16"></view>

      <button class="secondary-btn main-btn" bindtap="onLoginTap" loading="{{loading}}">
        登录 / 注册并登录
      </button>
    </view>

    <view class="login-benefits">
      <view class="benefit-item">
        <view class="dot"></view>
        <view>
          <view class="benefit-title">AI 整理成长记录</view>
          <view class="caption muted">自动生成每周成长总结和下一步建议。</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="benefit-item">
        <view class="dot"></view>
        <view>
          <view class="benefit-title">每日陪伴任务</view>
          <view class="caption muted">10 分钟就能完成的小任务，适合忙碌家庭。</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="benefit-item">
        <view class="dot"></view>
        <view>
          <view class="benefit-title">可视化成长看板</view>
          <view class="caption muted">老师与家长的记录一屏看清。</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

